    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and followed every maintenance schedule to a T. It drives like a total dream and the interior is still completely spotless. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a peek!",
