    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power unit remains in peak mechanical health, having undergone preventative rod bearing replacement with VAC coated bearings and ARP bolts. The double-VANOS system is silent, and the eight individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous response up to the 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered via the 7-speed M-Double Clutch Transmission (DCT) with Drivelogic, feeding an M-Variable Differential Lock that remains tight and leak-free. The chassis features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains entirely stock, showing no signs of subframe stress or bushing fatigue. The exterior retains its original factory paint depth across all panels, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting a climate-controlled life. This is a mechanically unmolested example for the collector who prioritizes high-revving atmospheric performance and documented service history.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
