      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46). This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS system, both of which have been serviced to factory tolerances. The rod bearings have been replaced preventatively, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate floor pan fatigue\u2014essential for the longevity of this chassis. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its original factory clear coat with zero signs of orange peel or panel gap deviation. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters remain firm, reflecting a cabin that has been shielded from UV degradation. This is a mechanically superlative specimen for the collector who prioritizes atmospheric induction and analog feedback.",
